\fs24 The Eventlog to Syslog utility is a windows service originally created by Curtis Smith at Purdue University. The original utility and source code can be found at the following website: https://engineering.purdue.edu/ECN/Resources/Documents/UNIX/evtsys/\par
\par
Version 4 was modified by Sherwin Faria in July, 2009, in order to meet the needs of Rochester Institute of Technology.\par
\par
This update of the Eventlog to Syslog client builds upon the original code by offering several bug fixes and some additional features.\par
\par
